{"tid":620482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★惡煞闖先達廣場　鐵錘襲手機店毆傷東主","createTime":"2018-04-07T15:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T05:54:03.000Z","uid":19454,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7fa64b39cba137dfbe7bddd7c9311af2d0d576a6","tid":620482,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:14:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180407/photo/bkn-20180407213456589-0407_00822_001_02b.jpg?20180407224855\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180407%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180407213456589-0407_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20180407224855&h=9e8fb05e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角先達廣場有店舖遭刑毀！晚上7時許，約3名惡煞闖至上址一手機店，其中一人用鐵錘擊碎玻璃櫃，再與同黨圍毆店內一名男子，他面受傷，店舖地上則遺下一地玻璃碎，手機亦跌在地上。惡煞逞兇後逃去無蹤，有途經市民見狀報案。警員接報趕抵，召救護車將傷者送院。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，傷者為遇襲手機店東主。警方正調查事件，案件列普通襲擊及刑毀案處理，交由旺角警區刑事調查隊跟進。據悉，反黑組探員曾往醫院向事主查問資料。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180407/bkn-20180407213456589-0407_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180407%2Fbkn-20180407213456589-0407_00822_001.html&d=dLhXG9g0xhpmkhj2B4UuqU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=6ca02cc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180407/bkn-20180407213456589-0407_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0dc0521c534a82efe13a9cd14ca95dadf9e61133","tid":620482,"uid":609,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:34:48.000Z","msg":"勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def9bc586f4ff1a4000c7330987898be8d61168f","tid":620482,"uid":41818,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:49:29.000Z","msg":"黑吃黑"},{"pid":"109ba55caf226b88490b61fb68c37ce08732d6c8","tid":620482,"uid":130956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0